            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1597161103406-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into thin chips, then add them to a baking tray with the <strong>dried oregano</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray in the oven for 25-30 min or until crisp</p><p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1597161109156-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1597161109156-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1597161109156-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1597161109156-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1597161109156-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Strip the <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them roughly, discard the stems</p><p>Grate <strong>half</strong> the <strong>cucumber</strong> and slice the rest into batons</p><p>Add the<strong> chopped garlic</strong>,<strong> chopped mint </strong>and <strong>grated cucumber</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> and mix it all together – this is your <strong>tzatziki</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1597161114710-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1597161114710-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
