          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1597161114710-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain the <strong>sliced red onion</strong> in a sieve and rinse under <strong>cold water</strong></p><p>Return to the bowl and add the <strong>white wine vinegar </strong>with a generous pinch of <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Stir to combine and set aside to pickle – these are your<strong> quick-pickled onions</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
